  "description": "<p>Job Scopes 工作范围</p>\n<p>1) Teaching lessons to various levels of classes 教课程 向不同级别的课程教授课程</p>\n<p>2) Class teacher in charge of all matters relating to children welfare and routine care 负责与儿童福利和日常护理有关的所有事项</p>\n<p>3) Assist other teachers to help out in other classes 协助其他老师，帮助其他班级</p>\n<p>4) Prepare lesson plans for the class(s) in charge 为负责的课程准备课程计划</p>\n<p>5) Excellent communication and classroom management skills 优秀的沟通和课堂管理能力</p>\n<p>6) 44-48 hours per week 每周 44-48 小时</p>\n<p>Salary Depending on Experience and Qualification</p>",
